                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900424-107-off556 t17900424-107-cd557"></join>, one piece of false and counterfeit money, of the likeness of half-a-guinea, knowing it to be forged and counterfeit, as and for a good half-guinea did offer to 
                     
                        <persName id="t17900424-107-victim978" type="victimName">
                           Susannah 
                           Carter
                        <interp inst="t17900424-107-victim978" type="surname" value="Carter"></interp>
