                     </persName>
                     
                  
               
                  </rs>.</p>
               <p>A second Count, for uttering another piece of false, counterfeit money and coin, made to the likeness of a shilling, as and for a good shilling, offering it to her, knowing it to be false.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17900424-107-person979">
                  SUSANNAH
                   CARTER
               <interp inst="t17900424-107-person979" type="surname" value="CARTER"></interp>
